This file records the various ipltd-specific kludges that have been
put in the software, which will need to be fixed if the software is to
be used by other companies.

* Location prompt in usestock.py/put_on_sale

Department 1 has been hard-coded.

* Coffee pot timer in extras.py

Department 11 has been hard-coded.

* Bar billiards checker in extras.py

Vat band 'A' has been hard-coded.

* Waste descriptions in recordwaste.py

Many waste descriptions have been hard-coded.  These should at a
minimum be referred to the config file!
